To gather streamwise_ruu statistics:
  1. copy lines [27,32] to your .usr file
  2. change TWO_POINTCORR to 1
  3. copy lines [143,168] to userchk file. Also make sure parameter(nstat=25) precedes this block.
  4. copy lines [446,537] to somewhere in your userchk subroutine

To go back to old mode:
  1. change TWO_POINTCORR to 0
